{"TopicId":29152,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"Low-ish Frontier - A KSP Board Game","CreatedByName":"Holo","CreatedById":39606,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T22:04:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Holo","CreatedById":39606,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T22:04:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m working on a kerbal space program board game, the working title of which is low-ish frontier. Here\u0027s some of what I\u0027ve made for it so far:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/bV9Bjrt.png\u0022 alt=\u0022bV9Bjrt.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/UVoY0uy.png\u0022 alt=\u0022UVoY0uy.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThose are planet cards, and the left side is the front, and the right side being the back. They give the info about planets, and the idea is that you place bases and landers atop these cards to amass points. I\u0027ve also probably broken all known rules of card design with it, so tell me if any changes need to be made.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-05-27T22:08:04Z\u0022 title=\u002205/27/2013 10:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EMay 27, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Holo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Westo454","CreatedById":12702,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T22:13:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECool, waiting to see some rules and more planets!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Holo","CreatedById":39606,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T22:29:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Westo454\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Westo454\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ECool, waiting to see some rules and more planets!\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks! Moho is about 80% done, and Minmus and the Mun are both around 30%. I\u0027ve also made a card for the Sun, which I\u0027ll upload when I\u0027m back at my computer.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI haven\u0027t started on the rules yet, but it will be orientated around increasing your industrial, scientific and military capabilities in space.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Needles_10","CreatedById":59554,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T22:48:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice use of the Knowledge Base descriptions.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Holo","CreatedById":39606,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-26T20:25:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/iefjhES.png\u0022 alt=\u0022iefjhES.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECard for the Sun.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMoho is still at 80% done, but I\u0027ve also got the Mun and Minmus 80% done too. Any cards you want me to do next?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Needles_10\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Needles_10\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ENice use of the Knowledge Base descriptions.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks! I didn\u0027t know what to stick on the front, and the knowledge base descriptors seemed perfect.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-05-26T20:31:58Z\u0022 title=\u002205/26/2013 08:31  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EMay 26, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Holo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Holo","CreatedById":39606,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-27T21:39:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/SAJMKco.png\u0022 alt=\u0022SAJMKco.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere\u0027s the card for Eve.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMun done\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/TE3MC0K.png\u0022 alt=\u0022TE3MC0K.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMinmus also done\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/wseF9LP.png\u0022 alt=\u0022wseF9LP.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-05-27T21:47:34Z\u0022 title=\u002205/27/2013 09:47  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EMay 27, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Holo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Needles_10","CreatedById":59554,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-27T21:52:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI cannot wait for the Bop card. I simply love the Knowledge Base description. (IT IS CANON!)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Holo","CreatedById":39606,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-27T22:03:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Needles_10\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Needles_10\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI cannot wait for the Bop card. I simply love the Knowledge Base description. (IT IS CANON!)\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAsk and ye shall receive:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/jasdwQR.png\u0022 alt=\u0022jasdwQR.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-05-27T22:07:15Z\u0022 title=\u002205/27/2013 10:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EMay 27, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Holo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atanar","CreatedById":59913,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-27T22:54:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThat just gave me an idea for another actual game. I will make a \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/showthread.php/32223-Another-Kerbal-Card-Game\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Enew thread.\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-05-27T23:16:22Z\u0022 title=\u002205/27/2013 11:16  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EMay 27, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Atanar\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Holo","CreatedById":39606,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-28T19:41:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/8vCiFMh.png\u0022 alt=\u00228vCiFMh.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat I\u0027ve done so far of the board. The lines show where your spacecraft can move; red is interplanetary transfers, gold is between moons. Jool is not yet finished.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"hoojiwana","CreatedById":57079,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-30T04:25:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWell this could be interesting. How much like High Frontier are you going to make it, or are you just using it as inspiration?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Panichio","CreatedById":2858,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-30T06:08:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022hoojiwana\u0022 data-cite=\u0022hoojiwana\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWell this could be interesting. How much like High Frontier are you going to make it, or are you just using it as inspiration?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPersonally, I wouldn\u0027t expect him to make it quite as detailed as High Frontier. Something along the lines of it but a little bit simplified would actually be a lot of fun. Can\u0027t wait to see more, Holo! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"capi3101","CreatedById":59027,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-31T16:44:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/showthread.php/32223-A-Kerbal-Card-Game?p=559923\u0026amp;viewfull=1#post559923\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMaking a repeat pitch\u003C/a\u003E in regard to developing this...\n"}]}